            size="+2">Evoked
            easily due to physical similarities. Should be avoided</font></font></li>
      <li><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><font size="5"><b>Desktop
              metaphor:</b></font><font size="+3"> </font><font
            size="+2">Once the most important metaphor, now slowly
